title: Renaming a Saved Filter - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
text: Click the Filter button and click the Saved Filter field to choose the filter of your choice. Once chosen, click Action and then click Rename . Enter the new filter name and click OK to save the changes.
